Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=======story=======
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你撲到我懷裡來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得我回來了 你這傢伙真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:36.46,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(174,890)}應有之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你從南美帶回來的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見嘛 你居然看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不看報紙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想費腦子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}…的強勢太平洋高壓所驅趕 將會有多處放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的計畫排得滿滿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計畫？什麼計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有份光坐著就能賺5000日元的兼職 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做？還是不做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去跟他們說你做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 在兼職的地方用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 這裡是折木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志啊 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎？他在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎 里志打電話找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎 之前借你的書看完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是看完了 希望你快點還我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天過去拿方便嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職收工之後可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職收工之後可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職？奉太郎你兼職？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你發什麼神經了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心血來潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替老姐的熟人看管市民泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你姐姐啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說你怎麼可能那麼勤勞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出門了 先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我之後過去取笑你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你便 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你們是三個人一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我聯繫了她們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是可以看到珍稀動物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 你說的就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 工作的奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實話說 我好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 難得來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起玩個開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別死盯著老子的女人看 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願別扯上我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 再游一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要開球了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同學 二傳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿千你不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同學 要接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要滑了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換班 你可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃午飯怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早點說 就能做更像樣點的午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話你最好對奉太郎說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為奉太郎簡直就是活生生的嫌麻煩集合體嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他突然勤勞起來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼能錯過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 像這樣大家聚在一起很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得不太相稱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼不相稱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池和奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太過分了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳裝和折木也不相稱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 還有太陽和奉太郎也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海和折木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有夏天和奉太郎之類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不能這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 回泳池去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那就把垃圾收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把椅子歸位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再去買一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將來的夢想會不會是成為游泳運動員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人裡說不定會出現能拿金牌的選手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可說不準
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只取決於那個人是否是能成為那種人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別的人就可以成功 而普通人則不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學想成為特別的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正 我始終是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學是特別的 對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學和摩耶花同學也很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我有關的人們 對我來說都是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的主觀想法就算了 我指的是一般而言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主觀不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必在意和周圍相比是普通還是特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得只要有一個人覺得自己是特別的就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.98,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}白露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.98,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}陰氣漸重 露凝而白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主觀不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 換班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是奉太郎份內的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認得那位穿紅色泳裝的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們剛吃完飯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的左耳上戴著個白色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 現在已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事真虧你能注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 注意到這個純粹是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 這又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一那個是耳環怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人踩到了 搞不好是要受傷的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學 能和我們一起找找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼大的地方找…沒開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定耳朵上戴著東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 在找之前應該先向本人確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想這麼做 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不太方便問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是要問什麼奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你去問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 你是監視員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 之前發火的那個人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 我不想把事情鬧大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就悄悄地找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我一個人辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我讓其他人來監視 你就到泳池邊巡邏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 泳池裡就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然也會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是分區負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你 拿出點幹勁來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 這簡直就像是白拿薪水的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少決定一下分工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 我來想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 台階那邊就由千反田同學和摩耶花負責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑梯那邊奉太郎來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳台就歸我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份兼職是非做不可的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 你沒想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的座右銘還真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太隨便對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總得有點反應啊 就算是牢騷也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則很無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我走了 回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是撿到彈珠拿來扔掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 看到現在的你就讓人洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說 你很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就別看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的你看了就讓人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然都很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過至少做回之前的你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能互相較勁還更好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還更好一點…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不過或許不找也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 奉太郎你知道些什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田 你看到的真的是耳環嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是非常清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 她的左耳確實有個白色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一邊有的話 說不定是耳飾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我要問的並不是飾品的種類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是她耳朵上的究竟是不是飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果耳朵上戴著東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她會這麼隨便地拍耳朵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是在她本人無意識的情況下附著上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣 那附上去的東西又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這個…里志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把伊原抱起來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 在這種地方抱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那讓千反田抱怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能因為是阿千就可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小孩子一樣 羞死人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想試試裝成小孩子的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 為什麼要做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了驗證我的假設
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指這件事的假設？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 我做成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同學力氣挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是按一般看法來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般會放在肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我可以下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我看到那位女性抱著那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們大概是母子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那孩子拿著冰淇淋被抱起來了會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 冰淇淋正好可能會沾到左耳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 現在它不見了是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳的時候掉了 或者是有人告訴了她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學的這一點 我還是覺得很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誇我也不會有好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得久違了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉太郎的挖苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見啊 你不挖苦我還要亂套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我還沒道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧出這麼大動靜 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿千 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我說那是耳環的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那——麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一放下心來就覺得肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 冰菓！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前說冰菓的原稿這次絕對會在明天給我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼說 應該說大致上好了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是還沒寫好吧 是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只能這麼說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 現在馬上回去寫稿子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我一定要盯著你直到寫完為止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 哎呀 就差最後一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人也可以搞定的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿千 折木 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能寫完就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呢 被人需要是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願他能好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人需要…我今天也依靠了折木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嗎 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也不壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道白色的東西就是冰淇淋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡沒有其他白色的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 倒是還有一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那我也告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職 還請你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換班了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
